The problem asks to prove that for any real numbers $\alpha$ and $\beta$, the limit inferior of $n \cdot \|n\alpha\| \cdot \|n\beta\|$ as $n \to \infty$ is 0. This is a well-known problem in mathematics, often referred to as the Littlewood conjecture.

